name: Universe #160
description: Universe #160 - Vesu had a unique flow around it as a growing mechanism. The flow filled the void of the universe and connected the living worlds of it together. A tired 160 found Vesu and the flow felt it's need for help. It pulled 160 to itself and nourished it with the rest of the universe. Their bond was ever strong as they became more and more inseperable as time passed.
